          "instruction": "Answer the questions based on the audio.",
          "prompt_html": "<h1>TABLE COMPLETION 02</h1><p>Use <strong>NO MORE THAN THREE WORDS</strong> for each answer.</p><p><strong>Survey size</strong>: Depends on total population size. A thousand individual surveys can reflect the total population.</p><table class=\"table-first-col-center\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Type of Survey</strong></th><th><strong>Advantages</strong></th><th><strong>Disadvantages</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Mail</td><td>Relatively <blank data-qid=\"q34\"/><br>Good for particular groups</td><td>Not good for decent response rate</td></tr><tr><td>Telephone</td><td>Good for when time and survey length are limited</td><td><blank data-qid=\"q35\"/></td></tr><tr><td>In-person</td><td>Good for collecting complex information</td><td>Can mean lots of <blank data-qid=\"q36\"/></td></tr><tr><td>Street interview</td><td><blank data-qid=\"q37\"/></td><td>Not scientific sampling</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"table-completion-merged-sections\"><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"4\" class=\"table-merged-label\">Survey content</td><td><strong>Questions can ask about:</strong><br>- opinions and attitudes<br>- factual characteristics or behaviour</td></tr><tr><td>Questions can be open-ended or of a <blank data-qid=\"q38\"/><br>type</td></tr><tr><td>Questions can be from 5 mins long to 1 hour +</td></tr><tr><td>Survey can use <blank data-qid=\"q39\"/><br>- interviewees can be questioned on two or more occasions</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"3\" class=\"table-merged-label\">Ethics</td><td>Results must not be used commercially</td></tr><tr><td>Individuals should not be mentioned</td></tr><tr><td>Results should be in <blank data-qid=\"q40\"/><br>(i.e. statistical tables or charts)</td></tr></tbody></table>",
